.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, purple, chestnut
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, sports, action
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, reggae, salsa
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, chess, reading
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the fan reggae##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is between the person watching sports movies and the fan gospel##2
4. the person who likes purple is the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Color    | emerald       | chestnut  | purple   |
| Movie-Genre     | sports    | action  | zombie |
| Music-Genre     | reggae   | salsa | gospel        |
| Hobby   | reading | fishing     | chess      |

