The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, handball, biathlon
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, german, argentine
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, electrician, police-officer
1. the argentine is on the left of the german##1
2. the software-developer is between the argentine and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
3. the person who's sport is basketball is the electrician##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the software-developer is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Flower          | amaryllis    | dahlia     | poppy      |
| Sport         | basketball | handball | biathlon |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german       | egyptian       |
| Job           | electrician     | software-developer       | police-officer     |

