.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting, basketball
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, alhambra, fonseca
3 different games are played: poker, domino, monopoly
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, turquise, light-blue
1. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the person playing domino is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who likes turquise##2
4. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Sport          | weightlifting | sailing | basketball    |
| Cigar         | alhambra | fonseca      | oliveros |
| Game   | poker   | domino     | monopoly        |
| Color           | red      | light-blue       | turquise      |

