.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, chinese, argentine
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, cain, havana
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, baseball, golf
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the cain-smoker is between the argentine and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
5. the cain-smoker is between the havana-smoker and the person who's sport is sailing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Nationality          | argentine      | chinese   | polish |
| Cigar         | blend | cain | havana |
| Sport   | sailing      | golf | baseball   |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate         | 7up  | coffee       |

