.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, february, july
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, disaster, craftsman-climbing
There are 3 different nationalities: british, canadian, russian
House: victorian, futuristic, craftsman
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the futuristic house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the british is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's birthday is in july##2
5. the person who's birthday is in february is the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Birthday      | may       | february      | july      |
| Movie-Genre         | disaster    | craftsman-climbing | mystery      |
| Nationality           | russian | british     | canadian |
| House   | futuristic     | craftsman          | victorian       |

