.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, rowing, weightlifting
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, drawing, reading
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, september, february
House: cottage, futuristic, gothic-revival
1. the gothic-revival house is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in february##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the futuristic house##1
6. the futuristic house is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Sport      | skateboarding      | rowing | weightlifting     |
| Hobby          | drawing   | rock-climbing      | reading     |
| Birthday   | february  | may      | september |
| House     | cottage | gothic-revival        | futuristic     |

