.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-10::.
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, indian, american
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, february, april
City: london, miami, venice
House: cape-cod, craftsman, wooden
1. the japanese is on the right of the american##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in march and the indian##2
3. the person traveling to venice is the american##1
4. the person traveling to miami is the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the cape-cod house is the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Nationality       | indian       | american       | japanese    |
| Birthday         | april | february | march |
| City       | miami      | venice         | london |
| House   | cape-cod        | wooden            | craftsman  |

