.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo, weightlifting
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, march, october
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, goldfish
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, blueberry, pear
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person eating pear##1
3. the person eating blueberry is in the middle##1
4. the person eating blueberry is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in january##2
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Sport      | weightlifting     | water-polo | rowing      |
| Birthday         | march  | october       | january |
| Pet   | goldfish   | goat         | ferret     |
| Food   | cucumber | blueberry    | pear     |

