.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, train, trike
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, horse, chinchilla
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, azure, turquise
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, potato, broccoli
1. the person driving the train is the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
3. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the train is between the owner of the horse and the person who likes azure##2
6. the person who likes blood-red is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Transport      | airplane | train      | trike            |
| Pet           | goldfish | chinchilla | horse |
| Color   | azure     | turquise        | blood-red         |
| Food   | potato  | cucumber    | broccoli        |

