There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, grey, amber
1. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person who likes grey and the person who's birthday is in january##2
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the fan funk##1
3. the fan soul is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who likes grey##1
6. the fan funk is on the right of the fan soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| City      | boston    | liverpool          | hannover |
| Birthday          | january | december           | march        |
| Music-Genre           | electronic | soul | funk         |
| Color   | azure    | amber    | grey      |

