3 different games are played: chess, scrabble, whist
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, january, june
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, puzzles, video-games
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person playing whist and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is between the person playing whist and the owner of the pony##2
5. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Pet          | goat  | cat   | pony |
| Game   | whist  | scrabble     | chess |
| Birthday   | february | january | june   |
| Hobby     | video-games   | puzzles   | board-games      |

