.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, singing, filmmaking
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, game, bolivar
3 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, monopoly
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, mirinda
1. the game-smoker is between the person drinking mirinda and the pall-mall-smoker##2
2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing monopoly is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person drinking water is the person playing mah-jongg##1
6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Hobby   | singing | hiking  | filmmaking     |
| Cigar   | bolivar    | game | pall-mall |
| Game           | domino        | monopoly   | mah-jongg  |
| Beverage     | mirinda      | fanta   | water |

