.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bluemaster, fonseca
3 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, snooker
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, tennis, parkour
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, nigerian, thai
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the nigerian is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person playing snooker is the spanish##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
6. the fonseca-smoker is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar           | bluemaster   | fonseca   | tiparillo |
| Game   | snooker | backgammon   | canasta     |
| Sport   | tennis     | sailing      | parkour    |
| Nationality           | spanish | nigerian | thai    |

