.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, november
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, coach, lawyer
House: wooden, townhouse, farmhouse
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, argentine, british
1. the argentine is the farmhouse house##1
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the wooden house is between the person who's birthday is in april and the doctor##2
4. the townhouse house is the british##1
5. the polish is between the person who's birthday is in december and the townhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Birthday      | april | november     | december        |
| Job         | coach   | lawyer | doctor |
| House   | townhouse        | wooden       | farmhouse      |
| Nationality           | british           | polish    | argentine       |

