.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, january
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, hiking, traveling
City: colone, london, liverpool
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, dunhill, dannemann
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the davidoff-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to london is the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to colone is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the dannemann-smoker and the person traveling to london##2
6. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday        | october      | july | january |
| Hobby         | hiking     | traveling    | magic-tricks        |
| City       | london | liverpool   | colone   |
| Cigar   | davidoff          | dunhill     | dannemann       |

 